                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Having multiple copies of your passport, ID, and forms like your I-20 can help ensure
                                that you have a backup plan in
                                case any of them ever get lost or stolen. Having both digital and physical copies will
                                make them much easier to replace.
                                It also may be necessary to show proof of identity in some situations during your time
                                of study in the US, and carrying
                                the original document may not be practical.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
